tests.title: should perform drag-and-drop successfully
tests.fullTitle: End-to-End Tests.Drag and Drop Test.should perform drag-and-drop successfully
tests.body: async()=>{const dragAndDropPage=new import_DragAndDropPage.default;await dragAndDropPage.navigateTo("/drag_and_drop");const initialColumnAText=await dragAndDropPage.getColumnAText();const initialColumnBText=await dragAndDropPage.getColumnBText();await dragAndDropPage.dragElementAToElementB();await browser.pause(500);const newColumnAText=await dragAndDropPage.getColumnAText();const newColumnBText=await dragAndDropPage.getColumnBText();await expect(newColumnAText).toBe(initialColumnBText);await expect(newColumnBText).toBe(initialColumnAText)}
